{"tid":2500203,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國圍攻特斯拉再咬煞車失靈　結果肇事車主認了：是我自己超速","createTime":"2021-04-22T12:34:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T12:36:59.000Z","uid":295230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cb49846c26c38da53e6f1d5272ebe6cca16fa320","tid":2500203,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:34:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTeP7aT73rQy97834rKaVrMhW6cRJQwuoaF3vrhsYWiim?filename=8oYr87x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8oYr87x.jpg&h=adef8f6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國一名女子在上海車展大鬧特斯拉，加上中國官媒助陣砲轟，使得特斯拉近來在中國網路上飽受抨擊，前天江蘇省常州市一輛特斯拉追撞前車，也被網友指控欵似是「煞車失靈」，結果車主自己今天發文表示，煞車沒失靈，是自己超速釀禍，還稱讚特斯拉「感覺車的質量還挺好」。<br />\n<br />\n車主表示，因為當天早上睡過頭，因為已經和人約好，所以一路上超速行駛，在變換車道時可能當時貨車被自己車輛A柱擋到視線，當時沒留意到有車，等到切進內線後才看到對方，緊急鬆開油門、猛踩煞車，「但是我也知道來不及了，只能含淚撞了上去。」<br />\n<br />\n車主描述，自己的車頭卡到前方小貨車底下，引擎蓋和擋風玻璃受損，不過安全氣囊沒有爆開，應該還沒有撞到安全氣囊感應區，雖然車頭受損嚴重，但後方一點問題都沒有，讓他感覺特斯拉的質量還是很不錯，「煞車沒有失靈，氣囊沒爆我能理解，車子還是蠻香的，特斯拉維修服務中心很到位。」（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"dbc54edf3bdb1589ab1d9f69e2d2eb753bf89712","tid":2500203,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:34:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://weibo.com/3546875035/Kc5nTfG4z?filter=hot&amp;root_comment_id=0&amp;type=comment#_rnd1619094849220\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2F3546875035%2FKc5nTfG4z%3Ffilter%3Dhot%26root_comment_id%3D0%26type%3Dcomment%23_rnd1619094849220&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrRzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=cf3a275b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://weibo.com/3546875035/Kc5nTfG4z?filter=hot&amp;root_comment_id=0&amp;type=comment#_rnd1619094849220</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210422/XO4OJXXDTJCLJH2M5LEP5NPHWY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210422%2FXO4OJXXDTJCLJH2M5LEP5NPHWY%2F&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrRzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=65d1c955\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210422%2FXO4OJXXDTJCLJH2M5LEP5NPHWY%2F&h=26344d70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210422/XO4OJXXDTJCLJH2M5LEP5NPHWY/</a>"},{"pid":"85e9bfb3f515e964b66ad826ff2bfe1cc6f14d63","tid":2500203,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:35:18.000Z","msg":"習帝講過要彎道超車，超速又有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8455e99c63fdb8e6430fdc44644cbb9c99451f2","tid":2500203,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:36:59.000Z","msg":"已經過左數俾車主 或者黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}